System Workflows
User Flow

User registers and logs in

Reports a breakdown and selects issue type

Shares live GPS location

System assigns nearest technician

Live tracking until issue resolution

Optional journey continuation via rental/taxi

Technician Flow

Technician logs in

Receives service request

Accepts assignment

Live location tracking enabled

Completes service and closes request

Admin Flow

Monitor all active requests

Manage technicians and services

Configure pricing

Analyze system performance

